=========================================================
  PROJECT MODULE — ALL ENDPOINTS
=========================================================

Base URL: /api/v1/projects
Permission prefix: projects.*

--- PROJECTS (CRUD + Stats) ---

GET    /projects/stats                          ProjectController@stats              projects.projects.view
GET    /projects                                ProjectController@index              projects.projects.view
GET    /projects/{id}                           ProjectController@show               projects.projects.view
POST   /projects                                ProjectController@store              projects.projects.create
PATCH  /projects/{id}                           ProjectController@update             projects.projects.edit
DELETE /projects/{id}                           ProjectController@destroy            projects.projects.delete

  show returns toDetailArray() which includes:
    - project fields (name, project_code, description, objectives, status, etc.)
    - project_manager (name, resolved from employee)
    - department (name, optional — nullable)
    - total_budget, currency
    - start_date, end_date, location
    - team_member_count, activity_count, budget_line_count, donor_count, partner_count, note_count
    - activity_progress (% completion)
    - Full arrays: donors[], partners[], team_members[], activities[], budget_lines[], notes[]

  stats returns:
    - total, draft, active, on_hold, completed, closed counts
    - total_budget (sum of non-closed)
    - by_department breakdown

  Required fields for create: name, start_date
  Optional: description, objectives, department_id, project_manager_id, end_date, location, currency, status, notes

--- BUDGET CATEGORIES ---

GET    /projects/budget-categories              BudgetCategoryController@index       projects.budget_categories.view

--- DONORS (nested under project) ---

GET    /projects/{projectId}/donors             ProjectDonorController@index         projects.projects.view
POST   /projects/{projectId}/donors             ProjectDonorController@store         projects.projects.edit
PATCH  /projects/{projectId}/donors/{id}        ProjectDonorController@update        projects.projects.edit
DELETE /projects/{projectId}/donors/{id}        ProjectDonorController@destroy       projects.projects.edit

--- PARTNERS (nested under project) ---

GET    /projects/{projectId}/partners           ProjectPartnerController@index       projects.projects.view
POST   /projects/{projectId}/partners           ProjectPartnerController@store       projects.projects.edit
PATCH  /projects/{projectId}/partners/{id}      ProjectPartnerController@update      projects.projects.edit
DELETE /projects/{projectId}/partners/{id}      ProjectPartnerController@destroy     projects.projects.edit

--- TEAM MEMBERS (nested under project) ---

GET    /projects/{projectId}/team               ProjectTeamMemberController@index    projects.projects.view
POST   /projects/{projectId}/team               ProjectTeamMemberController@store    projects.projects.edit
PATCH  /projects/{projectId}/team/{id}          ProjectTeamMemberController@update   projects.projects.edit
DELETE /projects/{projectId}/team/{id}          ProjectTeamMemberController@destroy  projects.projects.edit

  Team member fields: employee_id (required, unique per project), role (default 'member'), start_date, end_date, notes

--- ACTIVITIES (nested under project) ---

GET    /projects/{projectId}/activities         ProjectActivityController@index      projects.activities.view
POST   /projects/{projectId}/activities         ProjectActivityController@store      projects.activities.create
PATCH  /projects/{projectId}/activities/{id}    ProjectActivityController@update     projects.activities.edit
DELETE /projects/{projectId}/activities/{id}    ProjectActivityController@destroy    projects.activities.delete

--- BUDGET LINES (nested under project) ---

GET    /projects/{projectId}/budget-lines       ProjectBudgetLineController@index    projects.budget.view
POST   /projects/{projectId}/budget-lines       ProjectBudgetLineController@store    projects.budget.create
PATCH  /projects/{projectId}/budget-lines/{id}  ProjectBudgetLineController@update   projects.budget.edit
DELETE /projects/{projectId}/budget-lines/{id}  ProjectBudgetLineController@destroy  projects.budget.delete

  Adding/updating/deleting budget lines auto-recalculates project total_budget

--- NOTES (nested under project) ---

GET    /projects/{projectId}/notes              ProjectNoteController@index          projects.notes.view
POST   /projects/{projectId}/notes              ProjectNoteController@store          projects.notes.create
PATCH  /projects/{projectId}/notes/{id}         ProjectNoteController@update         projects.notes.edit
DELETE /projects/{projectId}/notes/{id}         ProjectNoteController@destroy        projects.notes.delete

--- PROJECT REPORTS ---

GET    /reports/projects/summary                ProjectReportController@summary           reports.reports.view
GET    /reports/projects/{id}/detail            ProjectReportController@detail            reports.reports.download
GET    /reports/projects/budget-utilization     ProjectReportController@budgetUtilization  reports.reports.view
GET    /reports/projects/activity-progress      ProjectReportController@activityProgress   reports.reports.view

  All report endpoints support ?format=csv|excel|pdf for download

NOTE: Projects are standalone (department_id is optional/nullable).
      Only name and start_date are required to create a project.
      Project manager and team members are optional.

